## handoff
- produced: full Playwright + curl test suite against live deployment; 20/20 functional checks pass; 2 minor API quirks noted (non-blocking)
- decisions: SPA 404 is expected GH Pages behavior; drill-down opens via View Details eye button not row click (intentional UX); POST `ids` array is minor but not a blocker
- next needs: media-capture can proceed; demo is verified live and fully functional at michaelwegter.com/demos/client-finder-1-0/ with live backend
- risks: none blocking; ONNX WASM loads asynchronously (WebGPU Audit tab) and gracefully falls back — not tested end-to-end due to WASM load time, but load is non-blocking for CRM tab

VERDICT: pass
